consulted me i am very uncomfortable however with the situation 
because normally i never discuss the identity of my clients and i 
never discuss their affairs 
i am a serious scientific astrologer and i am really not one 
of these clowns and i really dont like this circus atmosphere 
said ms quigley who has been practicing astrology since 1960 and 
has written three books on the subject 
jayj jacobs a member of the board of directors of the 
association for astrological networking said ms quigley is a 
