guidance he got when he signed on with dukakis in 1987 
the first thing he said was dont be negative about the hopes 
for the country and dont be overly negative about the reagan 
administration woodward told the washington post writer that 
dukakis described a problem he saw in the 1980 and 1984 
campaigns the overpreoccupation with what the united states cant 
