leader at the airport he arrived from uruguay on a boeing 727 of 
the state airline lloyd aereo boliviano at 516 pm 
the pontiff a skier spoke in a strong voice and showed no 
outward signs of being affected by altitude sickness which 
bolivians call sorocche la paz is the worlds highest capital 
and the altitude makes many visitors uncomfortable if not ill 
however in a meeting with bolivias 39 bishops at the end of 
the day the pope seemed to be wearying bishop julio terrazas 
head of the local episcopal conference did not deliver a prepared 
speech to the pontiff because we see that the pope is tired 
i believe these words have no place right now because of the 
weariness that your first day here has caused to the holy father 
terrazas said to the pope he instead handed the pope a copy of the 
speech 
in the text of terrazas speech he told the pope bolivia 
suffers from a situation of injustice that consumes thousands of 
brothers in degrading misery and inhumane unemployment to this are 
added other ills such as delinquency immorality and drug 
trafficking and other social calamaities that constitute a 
devastating scourge to the very being of our people 
