on this date 
in 1602 cape cod was discovered by the english navigator 
bartholomew gosnold 
in 1886 poet emily dickinson died in amherst mass 
in 1911 the us supreme court ordered the dissolution of 
standard oil co ruling it was in violation of the sherman 
